Note:
Runa Standard Library: iOS Development

Production-grade iOS development framework providing comprehensive
native iOS capabilities with modern Swift and Objective-C patterns.

Features:
- UIKit and SwiftUI component integration
- View Controller lifecycle management
- Auto Layout and constraint-based layouts
- Storyboard and programmatic UI development
- Core Data integration for local storage
- UserDefaults and Keychain services
- URLSession networking with modern async/await
- Core Location and MapKit integration
- Push notifications via Apple Push Notification Service (APNs)
- In-App Purchases and StoreKit integration
- Core Animation and advanced animations
- AVFoundation for media capture and playback
- Core ML and Vision framework integration
- HealthKit and fitness data integration
- CloudKit for cloud synchronization
- Background app refresh and multitasking
- iOS 16+ features and backwards compatibility
:End Note

Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "../../string" as String
Import "../../datetime" as DateTime

