Process called "add_binding_variable" that takes view as SwiftUIView and variable_name as String and binding_source as String:
    Set view.binding_variables[variable_name] to binding_source

Process called "create_navigation_view" that takes content_view as SwiftUIView and title as String returns SwiftUINavigationView:
    Return SwiftUINavigationView with:
    content_view as content_view
    navigation_title as title
    navigation_bar_title_display_mode as "automatic"
    navigation_bar_hidden as false

Process called "create_tab_view" that takes tab_items as List[SwiftUITabItem] returns SwiftUITabView:
    Return SwiftUITabView with:
    tab_items as tab_items
    selected_tab as 0
    tab_view_style as "automatic"

